    "description": "Sonata Software, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Full Stack Developer for our Allahabad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sonata Software:\nSonata Software is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Go\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sonata Software!",
